# SPA fallback rules for Cloudflare Pages.
#
# We don't use a /* catch-all because Cloudflare's Astro framework preset
# auto-applies its own SPA fallback to /index.html (the landing page) for
# unknown routes, which shadows broad wildcards. Listing each SPA route
# explicitly avoids the conflict.
#
# Static files take precedence over these rules, so /login, /signup,
# /onboarding (generated by [...slug].astro) are served directly without
# needing rules here.

# /app resolver
/app          /spa/  200
/app/*        /spa/  200

# Public booking + share links
/share/*      /spa/  200
/book/*       /spa/  200

# Org dashboard routes (/:orgSlug and /:orgSlug/calendar etc.)
/:org         /spa/  200
/:org/*       /spa/  200
